&lt;p&gt;* AUROC confidence intervals were within 0.0003 of the reported value.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Details regarding these performance comparisons can be found in my thesis, available through the Oxford Research Archive, titled 
&lt;a href=&#34;http://ora.ox.ac.uk/objects/uuid:2486465e-8fda-47a9-b82e-c0a93f4f1fc4&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Mortality prediction and acuity assessment in critical care&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;code&#34;&gt;Code&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This code is provided to ease the calculation of OASIS. If you have code for calculating OASIS in a different programming language, I would be happy to post it here and provide credit.&lt;/p&gt;
